OL,3,CChina spies jailed for 'shadow police'
OL,4,Coperation
OL,6,FTwo men were sentenced to a collective
OL,7,F18 years in prison at the Old Bailey
OL,8,Ftoday, on conviction of spying for
OL,9,FChina in the UK.
OL,11,FPeter Wai, from east London was jailed
OL,12,Ffor ten years and Bill Yuen, from
OL,13,FStaines, for eight years.
OL,15,FThe pair are the first to be convicted
OL,16,Fof spying for China under the 2023
OL,17,FNational Security Act.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
