CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781975953
OL,3,CChina spies jailed for 'shadow police'
OL,4,Coperation
OL,6,FThe Commander for Counter Terrorism
OL,7,FPolicing London, Helen Flannagan spoke
OL,8,Fto ITV News London about the
OL,9,Fsignificance of this first conviction.
OL,11,FShe said she wants to send a clear
OL,12,Fmessage about "our ability to send the
OL,13,Ffull force of the national security
OL,14,Fact, and bring those individuals to
OL,15,Fjustice."
OL,17,FWatch: Helen Flanagan speaks to ITV
OL,18,FNews London about the investigation
OL,19,Fand conviction.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
