CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781975953
OL,3,CChina spies jailed for 'shadow police'
OL,4,Coperation
OL,6,FPeter Wai conducted "shadow policing"
OL,7,Foperations on Hong Kong pro-democracy
OL,8,Fprotesters and dissidents living in
OL,9,Fthe UK on the orders of his superior
OL,10,FBill Yuen.
OL,12,FHe abused his position to gather
OL,13,Fintelligence on targets and was asked
OL,14,Fto pay "special attention" to British
OL,15,Fpoliticians, including senior Tory MP
OL,16,FSir Iain Duncan Smith.
OL,26,@nD@UOUnD@eO]vD@HOUvD@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
