OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781975953
OL,3,CChina spies jailed for 'shadow police'
OL,4,Coperation
OL,6,FAt the time, the former Metropolitan
OL,7,FPolice officer Wai was working at
OL,8,FHeathrow Airport for the UK Border
OL,9,FForce, as a special constable with
OL,10,FCity of London Police, and had set up
OL,11,Fa private security firm.
OL,13,FHis taskmaster and handler, ex-Hong
OL,14,FKong superintendent Yuen, was a senior
OL,15,Fmanager at the Hong Kong Economic
OL,16,FTrade Office in London, said to be an
OL,17,Fextension in the UK of the Hong Kong
OL,18,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781975953
OL,3,CChina spies jailed for 'shadow police'
OL,4,Coperation
OL,6,FYuen was linked directly back to the
OL,7,FChinese Security Bureau through his
OL,8,Fcontact with another ex-police chief,
OL,9,Fthe Old Bailey heard.
OL,11,FWai and Yuen were arrested after a
OL,12,Ffailed bid to snatch a former Hong
OL,13,FKong resident, Monica Kwong, from her
OL,14,Fflat in Pontefract, West Yorkshire, on
OL,15,FMay 1 2024.
OL,17,FFollowing a two-month trial, the pair
OL,18,Fwere convicted of assisting a foreign
OL,19,Fintelligence service under the
OL,20,FNational Security Act 2023.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
