PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781975953
OL,3,CChina spies jailed for 'shadow police'
OL,4,Coperation
OL,6,FFormer Metropolitan Police officer Wai
OL,7,Fwas also convicted of misconduct in a
OL,8,Fpublic office by searching the Home
OL,9,FOffice computer system for people of
OL,10,Finterest to Hong Kong authorities.
OL,12,FWai and Yuen had been accused
OL,13,Falongside Matthew Trickett an
OL,14,Fimmigration enforcement officer and ex-
OL,15,FRoyal Marine, who was found dead in
OL,16,Fwoodland near Maidenhead, Berkshire, a
OL,17,Fweek after being charged.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/6
